  allNodes:
  - dialogueText: Hello, I'm british
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses: []
    isRootNode: 1
    editorPosition: {x: 300, y: 200}
    guid:
      Part1: 1371785725
      Part2: 1155082823
      Part3: 790721166
      Part4: 1571819100
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: Yeah, your deal, your story, why should I even keep talking to
      you?
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389322
    - rid: 6774952781063389323
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 818, y: 145}
    guid:
      Part1: 4061710421
      Part2: 1157530809
      Part3: 689992359
      Part4: 2139168062
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'All right, mister Mistery...

      We have some stuff in common,
      you and I'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389334
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1668, y: 62}
    guid:
      Part1: 1128017573
      Part2: 1252307847
      Part3: 2114866107
      Part4: 1501563185
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Ha! Bold, I like it.

      Sure, I''ll tell you something about
      myself'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389324
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1668, y: 271}
    guid:
      Part1: 1835412929
      Part2: 1133826685
      Part3: 4086251931
      Part4: 1568069625
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'I''m a reporter from the city.

      Trying to find the tastiest
      stories around here.

      Ironic, isn''t it? given my previous job'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389325
    - rid: 6774952781063389326
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2234, y: 271}
    guid:
      Part1: 4197549194
      Part2: 1106058806
      Part3: 3232978570
      Part4: 3513204700
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Lucklily I''m not anymore!

      My fingers would cram if I had
      to put into words the inadequacy with which the Chef made lunch today.

      That
      borshch was truly abhorrent...'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389335
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2920, y: 462}
    guid:
      Part1: 3941858783
      Part2: 1303965904
      Part3: 1164245432
      Part4: 1086083098
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: Well my dear, like opening a can of food before it's its moment
      to be devoured, I wouldn't want to spoil the surpise
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389336
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2976.0508, y: 271}
    guid:
      Part1: 3083354042
      Part2: 1306995897
      Part3: 2998380477
      Part4: 334009166
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'I''m in the midst of getting my biggest pubiclation yet!

      Something
      so austanding that''ll surely shock''em all!'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389337
    - rid: 6774952781063389338
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2241, y: 62}
    guid:
      Part1: 2518043290
      Part2: 1126568364
      Part3: 3635081140
      Part4: 170371118
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'My boss for once!

      I swear I had enough evidence to libel
      that good for nothing bastard for life!'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389339
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2949, y: -104}
    guid:
      Part1: 2741510385
      Part2: 1272281206
      Part3: 642955931
      Part4: 3670528884
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Oh, don''t worry! I''ll make sure to <b>catch<\b> him red handed
      next time.

      That''s all, just a few more pictures and no one will ever
      call me obsessed again!'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389340
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 3697.0005, y: -104.00003}
    guid:
      Part1: 2660714080
      Part2: 1095029720
      Part3: 793529742
      Part4: 659547332
    tag: 
